<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-03-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-03-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="5" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d5">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">Hopkins Papers: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Prime Minister <persName type="from">Churchill</persName> to the President’s Special
                                    Assistant</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Hopkins</hi></persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d5fn1">Manner
                                    of transmission not indicated, but presumably via military
                                    channels.</note>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#left">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                                </seg>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-03-20">March 20,
                                    1943</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>From Prime Minister to Mister Harry Hopkins personal and most
                                secret.</p>
                            <p>I am hoping to receive a reply to my telegram to you of February 27
                                about <gloss target="#t_TubeAlloys1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Tube Alloys</hi></gloss>. Time is passing
                                and collaboration appears to be at a standstill. We have made some
                                progress in the last three months.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <gloss target="#t_Prime1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Prime</hi>
                                    </gloss>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>